Key management tasks:
* Key generation
  Key revocation
* key inspection
    looking at meta data on other keys
* Key import from identity providers 
  
  (* denotes local on the extension)

Identity Types:
  Email
  Social network: (Have Friends/ACL's built in)
    Facebook
    G+
    Diaspora
    Twitter
    
Can ask social networks about identity to see if there is consensus
  
Does not depend on them implementing our system, nor does it make them an
authoritative identity provider since there is a layer above them.

